name: Exuberance No. 6 Multiplicity
description: Celestial heavens shine brightly to bring Exuberance No. 6 Multiplicity to life in a triumph of colors. Exuberance No. 6 Multiplicity is a one-of-a-kind artistic collaboration that intertwines Tery Spataro's flower photographs and the artificial intelligence of Playform.io to give life to this transfixing new creation. The Exuberance art series are physical surface designs.
